data.description: *ELIGIBLE FOR AN FHA LOAN ASSUMPTION AT 2.75% INTEREST RATE, subject to buyer meeting qualification requirements. **OFFERING $2500 IN SELLER CONCESSIONS** Location, location, location! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the Gardens of Hollywood Park is centrally located and ready for its new owner! HVAC and roof were both recently replaced (May/June 2023). As you enter through the front door, there is a formal dining room with plenty of room for hosting. The entryway boasts high ceilings and brings you into the open concept living room, kitchen, and secondary eating space. This open space is flooded with natural light with a full wall of windows on one side, giving it a light and airy feel. The kitchen contains granite countertops, built-in oven and microwave, gas cooktop, bar seating, and the refrigerator coveys with the property as well. A stone fireplace gives the living room a cozy feel, while the crown molding and details give a touch of elegance. The master bedroom, with en suite bathroom, has tray ceilings with crown molding and multiple windows to let in natural light. The master bathroom has a double vanity, separate garden tub, and walk in shower. The 3rd bedroom offers the flexibility to function as either a bedroom or a study to fit your needs. A few additional features of this home: tile throughout (no carpet), oversized covered patio, and built in shelving in the garage.
